---
import LabBench from '../layouts/LabBench.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<LabBench title={`Games | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Interactive mini-games and experiments">
	<style>
		.games-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
			gap: 4rem;
			padding: 2rem 0;
		}
		.game-card {
			background: var(--surface-color);
			border: 1px solid var(--accent);
			border-radius: 8px;
			padding: 1.5rem;
			text-align: center;
			transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
			text-decoration: none;
			color: var(--text-color);
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			height: 100%;
			position: relative;
			overflow: hidden;
		}
		.game-card:hover {
			transform: translateY(-4px);
			box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
		}
		.game-card h3 {
			margin-top: 0;
			color: var(--accent);
			font-family: var(--font-ui);
		}
		.game-card p {
			color: var(--gray);
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			flex-grow: 1;
			font-family: var(--font-ui);
		}
		.status-badge {
			background: var(--surface-color);
			color: var(--gray);
			padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
			border-radius: 4px;
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			display: inline-block;
			margin-top: 1rem;
			border: 1px solid var(--gray);
			font-family: var(--font-ui);
		}
		.play-now {
			background: var(--accent);
			color: var(--bg-color);
			border: none;
			font-weight: bold;
		}
		
		/* Scanline effect for cards */
		.game-card::before {
			content: "";
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
			background: linear-gradient(
				to bottom,
				transparent 50%,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 51%
			);
			background-size: 100% 4px;
			pointer-events: none;
			opacity: 0.3;
		}
	</style>

	<div class="games-grid">
		<a href="/games/data-dice" class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸ² Data Dice</h3>
			<p>Explore probability distributions through interactive dice rolling. Watch the law of large numbers in action.</p>
			<span class="status-badge play-now">Initialize Module â†’</span>
		</a>

		<a href="/games/redaction-racer" class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸ•µï¸ Redaction Racer</h3>
			<p>Classified documents are leaking! Redact sensitive keywords before they reach the public domain.</p>
			<span class="status-badge play-now">Initialize Module â†’</span>
		</a>

		<a href="/games/data-bouncer" class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸ›¡ï¸ Data Bouncer</h3>
			<p>You are the firewall. Approve or deny data access requests based on role-based access control.</p>
			<span class="status-badge play-now">Initialize Module â†’</span>
		</a>

		<div class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸ§® Numerical Playground</h3>
			<p>Interactive demonstrations of numerical impermanence concepts and floating point oddities.</p>
			<span class="status-badge">Offline</span>
		</div>

		<div class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸ“Š Query Builder</h3>
			<p>Visual SQL query constructor and optimizer. Build complex joins visually.</p>
			<span class="status-badge">Offline</span>
		</div>

		<div class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸŒ Data Mesh Simulator</h3>
			<p>Simulate data mesh architectures, domain interactions, and data product lifecycles.</p>
			<span class="status-badge">Offline</span>
		</div>

		<div class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸ¯ ETL Puzzle</h3>
			<p>Challenge yourself with data transformation puzzles. Connect sources to sinks.</p>
			<span class="status-badge">Offline</span>
		</div>

		<div class="game-card">
			<h3>ğŸ”® Forecasting Lab</h3>
			<p>Interactive time series forecasting experiments. Test different models against datasets.</p>
			<span class="status-badge">Offline</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</LabBench>
